title: Tennessee Spatial Data Server, Interstate Highway Ramps, Tennessee, 2006
name: Tennessee Spatial Data Server, Interstate Highway Ramps, Tennessee, 2006
description:
This is a data layer used to show the location of ramps along Tennessee interstates.
Due to a lack of a clear metadata form, there is very little information accompanying the data set.
